g.title: Isolated environment for development and testing schema changes.
Periodically sync dev with prod to ensure fresh, relevant testing environment. (neonctl branches reset ...)
Live database serving the production application.
Developer edits schema definitions using Drizzle ORM syntax.
Drizzle Kit creates SQL migration files based on schema.ts changes.
Generated SQL migrations are executed against the dev branch.
Thoroughly test application compatibility and data integrity.
Validated migrations are executed against the production branch, often via CI/CD.
Automated deployment process that can include the production migration step.

g.text: If Tests Pass: Promote to Prod Pipeline
